      *  ED0175 - Bulk Transfer : Loans file special processing       *
      *                                                               *
      *  Function: Program creates bulk transfer batches for Midas    *
      *            Loans from files PF/CLOANCL and PF/CLOANCK.        *
      *            The DTA Preamble type used is the Drip Feed type,  *
      *            NOT the bulk transfer type.  This is not the same  *
