      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: EDC0020 - Bulk Transfer Component                 *
      *                                                               *
      *  Calls:     AOBANKR0 - Access Object for Bank Details ICD     *
      *             AOMEXPR0 - Access Object for ED ICD               *
      *             EDC0024  - Bulk Transfer Member Creation          *
      *                                                               *
